#: src/octoprint/plugins/gcodeviewer/templates/gcodeviewer_settings.jinja2:8
msgid ""
"If provided, the GCode Viewer will search for a line beginning with this "
"string. If found, all GCode up to that point will be skipped. This can be "
"used to skip \"purge/nozzle wipe\" GCode in the viewer. Note the search is "
"case sensitive."
msgstr ""
