msgstr "Folder checkout OctoPrint"

#: src/octoprint/plugins/softwareupdate/templates/snippets/checkoutFolder.jinja2:5
msgid "This needs to be set if you select commit based version tracking."
msgstr ""
"Musi być ustawione, jeśli wybierzesz śledzenie wersji oparte na commitach."

#: src/octoprint/plugins/softwareupdate/templates/snippets/githubToken.jinja2:2
